cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
type: software
title: "OrgGraph: Unsupervised Organizational Knowledge Extraction and Agent Simulation from Email Corpora"
abstract: >-
  OrgGraph is a research codebase for recovering organizational structure from
  email metadata and content without supervision, evaluating multi-agent
  dialogue naturalness against single-LLM baselines, and comparing
  graph-structured (GraphRAG) versus vector-only retrieval for agent
  communication coherence. The repository contains the full pipeline (corpus
  filter, email embedding, LLM signal extraction, project/topic clustering,
  knowledge-graph construction, persona enrichment, RQ1 evaluation) and the
  multi-agent simulation runtime used for the RQ2 and RQ3 studies.
